'''Utsushikoo no Mikoto''' (内色許男命) is a figure in ancient [[Japan]], identified as the progenitor of the {{ill|Hozumi clan|ja|穂積氏}} and referred to as "Utsushikoo no Mikoto" in the ''{{ill|Kojiki|ja|古事記}}'' and as "Utsushikoo no Mikoto" (欝色雄命) in the ''{{ill|Nihon Shoki|ja|日本書紀}}.''

